SR NO. 17 ENROLLED
WHEREAS, Brooklyn plans to attend Louisiana State University to earn a bachelor's
degree in human movement sciences, and thereafter transfer to Louisiana State University-
New Orleans to pursue a degree in occupational therapy, reflecting her desire to serve others
through a meaningful healthcare profession.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
does hereby commend and congratulate Brooklyn Antoinette Kersey on being selected as
the 2025-2026 "Student of the Year" at Doyle High School in Livingston Parish.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to
Brooklyn Antoinette Kersey.
PRESIDENT OF THE SENATE
